title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of sync
description: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of sync (1GILQD5)
OB: When using the JarExporter module, the exported JAR file includes itself, causing the application to go out of sync.
EB: The exported JAR file should not include itself to prevent the application from going out of sync.
SR:
1. Launch the application.
2. Use the JarExporter module to export the application as a JAR file.
3. Verify that the exported JAR file does not include itself.
